tafsir[1]{c,v,t}:
  2,142,"In the Hereafter, they will be shorn of the artificial supports on the strength of which they had remained careless of the Truth. Then it will be pointed out how the Truth had appeared before them and how they had rejected it with the help of false words how, though their mistake had been explained to them, they still thought that they had been successful in justifying their stand by clever misrepresentations."